---
title: Golden Chicken & Bacon Caesar-Style Salad with Garlic Roast Potatoes & Cherry BBQ Sauce
description: Let’s get this dinner started with crispy chicken bites and a cherry BBQ sauce to glaze the chicken so your mouth really starts watering. Toss it through the caesar-style salad with bacon and croutons, and get ready for a taste sensation!
